title: MyKetoBrain
description:
Elevate your keto journey with our Keto Diet Planning App, designed for seamless nutrition management. With hundreds of nutritionist-approved recipes at your fingertips, tailor your meal plans to fit your unique dietary needs and goals. Enjoy personalized features like: 
- Tracking nutritional intake
- Setting dietary preferences
- Accessing detailed recipe information 
- Add ingredients from recipe details to a digital list to track what you need for your meal plan recipes.
- Add recipes to your favorites list
- Add your mood for the day once and check your past moods in the progress details.
- Get access to all App features and recipes through our auto-renewable premium subscription packages. The auto-renewable subscription can be canceled anytime after purchasing and you will get access to the package till the end of its validity. 
All premium packages include:
>Browse through more than 300 nutritionist verified recipes.
>Add your favorite recipes to a Favorites list
>Track missing ingredients from recipes using Ingredient log
>Track your progress towards your goal
>Stay aligned with the amount of macro you need to intake during the period
 The subscription packages available are: 
 >Essential steps (CHF 117): Unlock premium access for 3 months  
 >Balanced routine (CHF 220): Enjoy premium features for 6 months 
 >Healthy New lifestyle (CHF 350): Get 12 months of premium access

Dive into a world of keto-friendly meals that align with your health objectives, all without the hassle. Embark on a transformative path towards a healthier, more vibrant you. Start today and make every meal a step towards your ideal keto lifestyle.

Link to Terms of Use: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jNhqfCyqTHOWKVIwqU7kzMS4u880bQ1c/view?usp=sharing
